  "texts": [
    "Dealing with the complexities of cybersecurity requires a multi-faceted approach that combines these technologies with traditional methods and involves different stakeholders such as technologists, policymakers, and legal experts.",
    "By working together, we can ensure not only the effectiveness of these technologies but also their ethical and responsible use.",
    "Understanding the broader landscape of AI and ML applications in cybersecurity requires us to take a holistic perspective that goes beyond just the technical aspects.",
    "The future of effective cybersecurity lies in finding a harmonious balance between the speed and scalability of AI and the creativity, intuition, and ethical judgment of human expertise.",
    "By combining the strengths of both, we can take a more comprehensive approach to identifying, responding to, and preventing cyber threats."
